b'Schedule of Approved Holidays for UIC Fiscal Year 2019'
b'GROUP A:\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0Applies to all staff members except those listed under Group B:\n'
b'\xc2\xa0'
b'*This schedule grants three (3) gift days and one (1) excused/gift day over the December/January holiday break. Employees do not\nuse any accrued leave benefits during this time'
b'\xc2\xa0'
b'GROUP B:\xc2\xa0Applies to all employees working in essential units, including but not limited to the\nUniversity of Illinois Hospital and Clinics; Biologic Resources Laboratory; Campus Auxiliary Services;\nAcademic Computing and Communications Center (ACCC); Telecommunication Services; and the Office\nof the Vice Chancellor for Administrative Services, including Facilities Management, Capital Programs,\nParking Services, Environmental Health and Safety, Facility and Space Planning, and the UIC Police\nDepartment:\xc2\xa0\n\n'
b'* This schedule grants three (3) gift days and one (1) excused/gift day over the December/January holiday break. Employees do not use any accrued leave benefits during this time. Group B employees working in the hospital or clinics who work on the gift days must schedule alternate days off between January 1, 2019 and June 30, 2019. All other Group B employees required to work on the gift days are asked to schedule alternate days off between December 1, 2018 and June 30, 2019.'
